text: “dangnan cng xya hı thraphysmbati phwk khea læa xya hı luk «khxng phwk khea pen thi phungcı kæ cea thæ cring xallxh thrng txngkar thi ca lngthosʹ phwk khea dwy sing hela nan nı chiwit hæng lok ni læa thi ca hı chiwit khxng phwk khea xxk cak rang pi khna thi phwk khea pen phu ptiseth sraththa theanan
